snippet.title: [DOAXVV] New Venus Release! Introducing Shizuku
snippet.description:
○Official Site：https://game.doaxvv.com/en/lp.html
Shizuku has finally come to "DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation!" (Voice: Hina Youmiya)
The new Venus, "Shizuku," is a girl (fox spirit) with an ephemeral aura who has come to the Venus Islands in search of a place to belong.
She usually disguises herself in human form, but she cannot completely hide her fox spirit nature from the Boss.
Enjoy a vacation with "Shizuku," the new Venus with irresistibly cute fluffy ears and tail movements.


○Facebook：https://www.facebook.com/doaxvvstaff/
Game Information
○Title：DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation
○Platform：Windows PC (Steam,Johren) 
○Genre：Sports Vacation
○Release Date：Steam 10 April 2019 (Wednesday), Johren 1 July 2021 (Thursday)
○In-game purchases：Free to play/In-game purchases in Steam,Johren
○hashtag：#DOAXVV
